The Aguata local government area secretariat in Anambra State is currently on fire. According to sources close area where the building is located, the secretariat was attacked by some unknown gunmen. Anambra State Police Public Relations Officer (PPRO), DSP Tochukwu Ikenga, confirmed that the secretariat was on fire but said that the cause of the fire was yet to be ascertained. Details Laterâ€¦